Great American Management andInvestment Inc said its 80 pct-owned subsidiary agreed to buycertain assets of two subsidiaries of Standard Oil Co, for 40mln dlrs and the assumption of certain liabilities.    Great American Industrial Group Inc agreed to acquire allthe U.S. and United Kingdom assets of Pfaudler Co and the stockof certain Brazilian, Mexican, and West German subsidiaries ofKennecott Mining Corp, it said. Pfaudler and Kennecott aresubsidiaries of Standard Oil. Reuter&#3;